    <item>
      <title>日本暗示中国海鲜禁令或将很快取得突破</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/japan-eyes-deal-to-end-chinese-ban-on-seafood-imports-media-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本政府高级官员称，日本正与中国及国际原子能机构就福岛核电站附近海水检测进行谈判，这增加了北京方面可能放宽对日本海产品的禁令的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/japan-eyes-deal-to-end-chinese-ban-on-seafood-imports-media-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 01:28:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>核能复兴让日本首相候选人团结起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/nuclear-power-revival-unites-japan-s-prime-minister-contenders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本可能仍在努力应对福岛核灾难的深远影响，但争夺下一任领导人的政客们一致同意一件事：这个国家需要更多的核能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/nuclear-power-revival-unites-japan-s-prime-minister-contenders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
